data.description:
This exquisite property at 1661 Pierce St, St. Charles, IA, offers an unparalleled opportunity for those seeking an opulent and secluded lifestyle. Encompassing 29.5 acres, the property boasts a myriad of impressive features that make it an idyllic haven for relaxation and recreation.
The residence itself is a fully remodeled home that effortlessly blends modern comfort and style, featuring electric fireplaces and upgraded appliances. Complementing the home is a vast 48x100 heated recreational building, complete with a batting cage and a designated ''man cave'' for leisure and entertainment. Beyond the buildings, the property encompasses over 20 acres of lush pasture, providing ample space for livestock, farming, or outdoor activities. A private 1-acre pond is one of the property's most exceptional features. It is truly a unique property, offering the best of modern living, recreational amenities, and the serenity of nature. Additional information on utilities, property taxes, and the local school district is available upon request. The terms and conditions of this listing agreement have been negotiated between the seller(s) and the listing agent, with a specified listing duration and price. For inquiries or to schedule a viewing of this exceptional property, please contact the listing agent. Don't miss this rare opportunity to make this extraordinary property in St. Charles, Iowa, your own.
